                <h1>Harnessing Renewable Energy for a Sustainable Future</h1>
                <p>Renewable energy refers to energy derived from natural sources that are replenished at a faster rate than they are consumed. This includes solar, wind, hydro, and geothermal energy. By harnessing these clean alternatives, we can significantly reduce carbon emissions, combat climate change, and create a sustainable future for generations to come.</p>
